list.name: Changes
list.comment: -app7.py is a perfect working version. The previous versions all have some bugs. -Add some debug functions. -App7.py can use the input fitness record text. Generate fitness record form. And record the daily calories trend. It can also record the current exercise or rest of all parts of the body. If certain parts doesn't get enough exercise, it will remind you. And if certain parts need to rest, it will also remind you. This is displayed on the body part training hit. The hit value of each part will gradually decrease with time. There are also functions that can be generated through the current fitness status. By clicking Generate suggestions, It can generate corresponding fitness suggestions according to the current fitness situation.
